Package: zztable1
Title: Create "Table One" Summaries for Clinical Trials
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("First", "Last", email = "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides functions for creating "table one" summaries of baseline 
    data in clinical trials and observational studies. Features include handling
    of numeric and categorical variables, stratification, p-value calculations,
    and customizable output in LaTeX and HTML formats. Compatible with tidyverse 
    workflows and includes support for missing data and grouped summaries.
